function u(t){let n=1;do n*=2;while(n<t);return n===t}function f(t,n,e){return t*(1-e)+n*e}function i(t){let n=r(t),e=c(t);return n-t>t-e?e:n}function r(t){return t--,t|=t>>1,t|=t>>2,t|=t>>4,t|=t>>8,t|=t>>16,t++,t}function c(t){return t=t|t>>1,t=t|t>>2,t=t|t>>4,t=t|t>>8,t=t|t>>16,t-(t>>1)}function p(t,n,e=2){let o;switch(e){case 1:o=c(t);break;case 2:o=i(t);break;case 3:default:o=r(t);break}return Math.min(o,n)}export{u as a,f as b,i as c,c as d,p as e};
